---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div class="wplat-section">
    <h3 class="wplat-main-title">
        <Icon name="mdi:map-marker-question-outline" class="wplat-main-icon" />
        ¿Dónde puedo usar estos widgets?
    </h3>
    <div class="wplat-grid">
        <div class="wplat-card">
            <div class="wplat-card-header">
                <Icon name="mdi:wordpress" class="wplat-card-icon wplat-card-icon--wp" />
                WordPress
            </div>
            <p class="wplat-card-text">100% Compatible. Usa el enlace <strong>oEmbed</strong> (opción A) o el <strong>iFrame</strong> (opción B).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="wplat-card">
            <div class="wplat-card-header">
                <Icon name="mdi:web" class="wplat-card-icon" />
                Wix / Shopify
            </div>
            <p class="wplat-card-text">Busca el bloque "Incrustar sitio" o "HTML". Usa el enlace con <code>?widget=true</code>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="wplat-card">
            <div class="wplat-card-header">
                <Icon name="mdi:square" class="wplat-card-icon" />
                Squarespace
            </div>
            <p class="wplat-card-text">Añade un "Bloque de código" y pega el código <strong>iFrame</strong> completo.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="wplat-card">
            <div class="wplat-card-header">
                <Icon name="mdi:code-tags" class="wplat-card-icon wplat-card-icon--code" />
                Desarrollo a Medida
            </div>
            <p class="wplat-card-text">Funciona en todas partes. Solo copia y pega el código <strong>iFrame</strong>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .wplat-section {
        border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        padding-top: 2.5rem;
    }
    .dark .wplat-section {
        border-top-color: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
    }

    .wplat-main-title {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #0f172a;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
    .dark .wplat-main-title {
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .wplat-main-icon {
        width: 1.5rem;
        height: 1.5rem;
        color: #6366f1;
    }

    .wplat-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 640px) {
        .wplat-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
    }
    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .wplat-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        }
    }

    .wplat-card {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 1.25rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        transition: border-color 0.15s;
    }
    .wplat-card:hover {
        border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    }
    .dark .wplat-card {
        background-color: #18181b;
        border-color: #1e293b;
    }

    .wplat-card-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #0f172a;
    }
    .dark .wplat-card-header {
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .wplat-card-icon {
        width: 1.25rem;
        height: 1.25rem;
        color: #000000;
    }
    .dark .wplat-card-icon {
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .wplat-card-icon--wp {
        color: #21759b;
    }

    .wplat-card-icon--code {
        color: #6366f1;
    }

    .wplat-card-text {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #64748b;
        line-height: 1.625;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    .dark .wplat-card-text {
        color: #94a3b8;
    }
</style>
